- Yeah?
- Don't worry about it.

43:06.709 --> 43:08.460
Come on now, boy.

43:08.670 --> 43:11.213
Let's take your
whupping like a man.

43:12.757 --> 43:14.925
Kick his ass, Pete.
Watch him, Pete.

43:15.134 --> 43:18.720
Yeah, come on out here
and kick old sarge's ass.

43:18.930 --> 43:19.972
Come on, Geechee.

43:20.139 --> 43:23.308
You don't want the sarge
to grow old waiting for you now.

43:36.406 --> 43:37.990
Fight.

43:38.783 --> 43:40.450
Fight him. Fight him. Grab him.

43:41.619 --> 43:44.371
- Get him.
- Come on.

43:44.580 --> 43:46.665
Come on. Come on.

43:52.964 --> 43:55.132
Watch him, Pete.

43:58.594 --> 44:02.306
He got him. That got him.

44:02.640 --> 44:04.975
Come on. Get up. Get up, sarge.

44:06.060 --> 44:09.062
You throw
a pretty mean punch, boy.

44:09.272 --> 44:11.940
But old sarge is here
to kick your ass.

44:17.697 --> 44:20.324
- Come on.
- Come on, Pete.

44:20.533 --> 44:21.992
Move over there.

44:22.201 --> 44:24.870
- There you go.
- Come on.

44:25.038 --> 44:26.955
Who the hell is fighting over there?

44:28.207 --> 44:31.251
- Come on.
- There you go.

44:31.461 --> 44:34.421
- Get up, Pete.
- Get up, get up.

44:34.630 --> 44:38.383
- Get him, sarge.
- Vernon. Vernon.

44:41.220 --> 44:42.888
That's enough.

44:51.356 --> 44:56.401
Yeah, he beat me
pretty bad that day, sir.

44:57.779 --> 45:00.781
Did anybody report
the fight to an officer?

45:00.990 --> 45:04.076
No, sir, I never reported it.
I know I should have,

45:04.285 --> 45:07.704
but he left me alone after that
so I just played ball.

45:10.249 --> 45:12.751
I appreciate your honesty,
Peterson.

45:13.336 --> 45:15.003
Thank you, sir.

45:18.883 --> 45:22.344
Did you see Sergeant Waters
the night he was killed?

45:22.595 --> 45:25.639
No, sir. Smalls and I
had guard duty.

45:27.850 --> 45:31.103
Thank you. That'll be all for now.
Yes, sir.

45:33.064 --> 45:36.400
Did the team ever get
to play the Yankees?

45:36.609 --> 45:40.570
No, sir. We lost the last game
to a sanitation company.

47:35.478 --> 47:38.146
What brings you out to my
neighborhood, captain?

47:38.356 --> 47:39.731
Slumming?

47:40.066 --> 47:41.900
I wanted you to see the request

47:42.109 --> 47:46.029
I've sent to Colonel Nivens to have
your investigation terminated.

47:46.239 --> 47:49.491
Now, my reasons have nothing
to do with you personally.

47:49.700 --> 47:52.035
My request won't hurt
your career in any way.

47:52.245 --> 47:55.539
It's just that there are other
things to consider in this case.

47:55.748 --> 47:57.374
Only the color of my skin.

47:57.583 --> 47:59.918
Now, hold it, Davenport.

48:00.127 --> 48:02.671
I want the people that
killed Waters prosecuted.

48:02.880 --> 48:04.965
- So do I.
- Then give this up.

48:05.174 --> 48:08.718
White people down here, they
won't see their duty or justice.

48:08.928 --> 48:12.389
They'll see you. And you can't
possibly get at the truth.

48:12.598 --> 48:16.685
Why? Because two white
officers are involved in this?

48:16.894 --> 48:20.522
And you can't get them charged,
court-martialed or anything else.

48:20.731 --> 48:23.733
Why wasn't there any mention
of them in my report?

48:24.193 --> 48:26.945
You think I'm gonna let you
get away with this?

48:30.658 --> 48:33.910
I was ordered not
to include it.

48:34.537 --> 48:37.998
- By who?
- Colonel Nivens.

48:40.710 --> 48:42.419
Now, look,

48:42.628 --> 48:47.549
they took two .45-caliber slugs
out of Waters, Army issue.

48:47.758 --> 48:51.136
Now, if my men thought
a white officer had killed him,

48:51.345 --> 48:53.305
there would have been
a slaughter.

48:54.557 --> 48:56.474
Who are the officers?

48:56.684 --> 49:00.228
Lieutenant Byrd in Ordnance
and a Captain Wilcox,

49:00.396 --> 49:02.397
12th Hospital Group.

49:02.732 --> 49:04.899
Private Seymour saw them
on the road.

49:05.109 --> 49:08.361
When I checked the officers'
billet, I found them both asleep.

49:08.571 --> 49:11.740
They admitted they'd had an
argument with the sergeant...

49:11.949 --> 49:14.200
but said they'd left him
on the road.

49:14.410 --> 49:17.287
So you never believed
the Klan was involved.

49:17.496 --> 49:20.165
No. No.

49:20.374 --> 49:23.168
Now can you see why this
thing needs somebody else?

49:26.422 --> 49:28.173
Tell me what they told you.

49:30.593 --> 49:32.802
Look, hotshot,

49:33.179 --> 49:36.181
they're not gonna let you
charge those two men.

49:37.600 --> 49:40.101
Tell me what they told you.

49:41.812 --> 49:44.522
Left, hup, three, four.

49:44.732 --> 49:47.332
Left, hup, three, four.

49:56.994 --> 50:01.206
Left, two, three, four.

50:07.254 --> 50:11.132
You wanna move your ass off
the goddamn road, sergeant?

50:12.134 --> 50:14.886
Well, I'll be damned.

50:15.096 --> 50:18.390
If it ain't the white boys.

50:19.600 --> 50:21.017
Did you hear what he said?

50:21.227 --> 50:22.310
- Shit.
- Let it go.

50:22.520 --> 50:25.897
Let it go my ass.
Come here, sergeant.

50:26.107 --> 50:31.319
White boys,
all starched and stiff.

50:31.529 --> 50:36.282
Want everybody to learn
that symphony shit.

50:36.617 --> 50:39.035
That's what you said in France,

50:39.245 --> 50:42.956
and, you know,
I listened to it.

50:43.165 --> 50:45.291
Am I right, now? Am I?

50:45.501 --> 50:48.211
You'd better straighten up
and salute an officer

50:48.379 --> 50:50.588
or I'll take your
fucking stripes, boy.

50:51.465 --> 50:53.133
That's better.

51:01.142 --> 51:05.937
Well, look at the nigger.

51:06.147 --> 51:09.941
You come to attention right now,
and that is an order.

51:10.484 --> 51:14.654
I ain't doing nothing
white folks say do. No more.

51:14.864 --> 51:16.948
No, leave him alone,
the man is drunk.

51:17.158 --> 51:19.617
I want the nigger to
do like I tell him. Do it.

51:19.827 --> 51:21.786
- No.
- I'll teach him, goddamn it.

51:21.954 --> 51:24.205
I always mind y'all.

51:25.624 --> 51:28.168
Look what it's done to me.

51:29.420 --> 51:31.796
I hate myself.

51:32.006 --> 51:35.008
Don't blame me. God's the one
who made you black, not me.

51:35.217 --> 51:36.801
My daddy said,

51:37.762 --> 51:41.014
"Don't talk like this,"

51:41.390 --> 51:43.683
talk like that.

51:44.143 --> 51:45.351
Don't say,

51:47.730 --> 51:49.272
"Say..."

51:53.986 --> 51:56.196
I even killed for you.

52:01.577 --> 52:02.786
Stop!

52:03.537 --> 52:07.415
You wanna kill him? The man is sick.
Let him go. You're gonna kill him.

52:07.625 --> 52:12.086
Come on.

52:24.767 --> 52:27.519
White men are killing for you,
nigger.

52:29.605 --> 52:32.190
Good men dying for you.

52:37.822 --> 52:42.283
So anyway, they said
they left Waters about 2310.

52:44.703 --> 52:48.373
And everyone in the barracks
confirms that they were in by 2330

52:48.582 --> 52:51.709
and that neither man left
till the following morning.

52:52.545 --> 52:56.089
That's nothing but white officers
lying to protect two of their own.

52:56.257 --> 52:57.757
You know that.

52:57.925 --> 53:01.594
I'm arresting both of them, captain.
Consider yourself under arrest...

53:01.804 --> 53:04.389
pending my charges against you.
What charges?

53:04.598 --> 53:08.059
It was your duty to go over
Nivens' head if you had to.

53:08.269 --> 53:11.062
Oh, you're gonna arrest
the colonel too, Davenport?

53:11.272 --> 53:13.064
Because he's part
of their alibi.

53:13.274 --> 53:16.526
He was there in the officers'
billet when they came in.

53:16.735 --> 53:19.320
Played poker till 3:30
in the morning, yeah.

53:19.530 --> 53:24.158
Yeah, the colonel, Major Hines
and four other white officers.

53:24.368 --> 53:26.035
They're all lying.

53:26.245 --> 53:28.621
You just go out and prove it.

53:44.388 --> 53:48.016
Sir, I intend to arrest Lieutenant
Byrd and Captain Wilcox.

53:48.225 --> 53:51.185
You will do nothing of the kind.
Colonel.

53:51.395 --> 53:55.064
I believe these men had something
to do with Sergeant Waters' death.

53:56.650 --> 53:58.818
No, I can't allow that.

53:59.028 --> 54:02.155
You have no authority
to arrest white officers.

54:02.364 --> 54:05.074
Then give me the authority, sir.

54:05.284 --> 54:06.409
Colonel.

54:06.619 --> 54:08.912
Your breakfast is ready.

54:11.123 --> 54:12.874
Thank you, honey.

54:14.710 --> 54:17.337
Can I have someone
fetch you coffee, captain?

54:17.546 --> 54:20.173
No, thank you, ma'am.

54:23.177 --> 54:27.096
I hope they're making your stay at
Fort Neal real comfortable, captain.

54:27.431 --> 54:31.309
They're taking good care of me.
It's very thoughtful of you to ask.

54:33.854 --> 54:34.979
Good morning.

54:35.147 --> 54:37.357
No, I can't give you
that authority.

54:37.566 --> 54:40.360
- I told you.
- 30.

54:40.569 --> 54:41.736
I was there.

54:41.946 --> 54:45.114
Now, you've read
our affidavits on this thing.

54:45.324 --> 54:48.993
Colonel, what will the Army say
when they find out white officers

54:49.203 --> 54:52.330
beat up the victim not long
before he was shot to death?

54:52.539 --> 54:55.917
Their CO refuses to report
they had anything to do with it

54:56.126 --> 54:58.962
and he signs an affidavit
supporting their alibi.

55:00.339 --> 55:04.342
These two are our best suspects.
How can you not have them arrested

55:04.551 --> 55:07.720
or at least questioned
by the investigating officer?

55:11.308 --> 55:14.602
Something like this
is bound to get out.

55:17.064 --> 55:19.190
I didn't say
you couldn't question them.

55:20.192 --> 55:22.485
But I want
a white officer present.

55:22.695 --> 55:25.238
And I want everything
that's said reported to me.

55:25.447 --> 55:28.449
- Is that clear?
- Of course, sir.

55:37.334 --> 55:40.586
You're dismissed, captain.
Yes, sir.

